Comics.

00:06:30.539 --> 00:06:34.470
The controversial King of Pop approached Stan
Lee for his help - and Lee was actually willing

00:06:34.470 --> 00:06:38.330
- but the former Marvel president and chairman
wasn't in charge of the company at the time

00:06:38.330 --> 00:06:39.809
and Jackson's bid failed.

